OL,3,CReform to announce 'visa freeze' for
OL,4,Csome countries if deportees not
OL,5,Caccepted
OL,7,FReform UK will impose "visa freezes"
OL,8,Fon countries including Pakistan,
OL,9,FAfghanistan and Syria if they refuse
OL,10,Fto take back migrants with no legal
OL,11,Fright to stay in Britain, Zia Yusuf is
OL,12,Fexpected to announce.
OL,14,FThe party's new home affairs spokesman
OL,15,Fwill unveil plans for the "immediate
OL,16,Fsuspension of visa issuance" if the
OL,17,Fnations do not accept deportees, which
OL,18,Fwould also apply to Eritrea, Sudan and
OL,19,FSomalia.
