OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1771815821
OL,3,CReform to announce 'visa freeze' for
OL,4,Csome countries if deportees not
OL,5,Caccepted
OL,7,FReform is also pledging to replace
OL,8,Findefinite leave to remain with a
OL,9,Frenewable five-year work visa and
OL,10,Fdedicated spouse visa and create a new
OL,11,Fagency with the capacity to detain
OL,12,F24,000 migrants at a time.
OL,14,FThe party said costings would be set
OL,15,Fout at the event on Monday when asked
OL,16,Ffor its calculations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
