PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1771815821
OL,3,CReform to announce 'visa freeze' for
OL,4,Csome countries if deportees not
OL,5,Caccepted
OL,7,F"We will secure our borders, leave the
OL,8,FECHR (European Convention on Human
OL,9,FRights) and deport those here
OL,10,Fillegally. My message to the British
OL,11,Fpeople is simple: I will secure our
OL,12,Fborders and make you feel safe."
OL,14,FLabour said Britain was a "proud,
OL,15,Ftolerant and diverse nation", which
OL,16,Fstands in opposition to the "divisive
OL,17,Fpolitics stoked by Reform".
OL,19,FParty chairwoman Anna Turley said:
OL,20,F"Reform wants to divide our country,
OL,21,Fnot deliver for the British people.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@`O]vD@[OUwD@\O]xD@]OUyD@ZO]|D@
OL,26,AAOU
