CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1771815821
OL,3,CReform to announce 'visa freeze' for
OL,4,Csome countries if deportees not
OL,5,Caccepted
OL,7,F"Their plan to deport people who have
OL,8,Ffollowed the rules, worked hard and
OL,9,Fbuilt their lives here ` our friends,
OL,10,Fneighbours and colleagues ` is a
OL,11,Fdirect attack on settled families and
OL,12,Ffundamentally un-British."
OL,14,FShe added: "The British people are
OL,15,Fright to expect firm control of our
OL,16,Fborders ` with clear rules about who
OL,17,Fcan come here and swift action against
OL,18,Fthose with no right to be here `
OL,19,Falongside action to make our country
OL,20,Fsafe ` and that is what Labour is
OL,21,Fdelivering."
